650
00:40:21,679 --> 00:40:22,519
Plans changed.

651
00:40:22,679 --> 00:40:24,000
She's staying.

652
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,360
Staying?

653
00:40:25,519 --> 00:40:25,840
Yep.

654
00:40:26,239 --> 00:40:27,159
Good.

655
00:40:27,679 --> 00:40:29,599
People act like

656
00:40:29,639 --> 00:40:31,320
the rest of the world

657
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,840
